column4:
Hello there,

I would like to request on your end a formal quotation. Kindly indicate in your quotation the following:

- quote validity
- payment terms
- delivery lead time
- alternative offer (if applicable)

Your immediate response is highly appreciated.

Our updated order lists and company profile are enclosed for your convenience. kindly send us your best offer.

Best Regards

Rosa Oliveira
Senior Manager
Salamanca Retails
